thread.title: 美股盤後─經濟數據強勁 三大指數再創新高點 S&P 500連七天上漲
thread.title_full: 美股盤後─經濟數據強勁 三大指數再創新高點 S&P 500連七天上漲

posts.title: 美股盤後─經濟數據強勁 三大指數再創新高點 S&P 500連七天上漲
posts.text:
S&P 500 連七天上漲，創 5 月以來最長上漲期間。 
分析師說，股市持續獲得短期動能的支撑，S&P 500 在突破了 9 月整理走勢後，上升趨勢再度展開，當有助阻止回檔走勢。 道瓊工業平均指數收高 19.97 點或 0.09% 至 22661.64。 
Nasdaq 指數收高 2.91 點或 0.04% 至 6534.63。 
S&P 500 指數收高 3.16 點或 0.12% 至 2537.74。 
費城半導體指數收高 2.81 點或 0.24% 至 1185.24。 
週三，投資人反應主要的經濟數據。ADP 公司公布，美國私人企業 9 月新增就業 13.5 萬人，高於預估的 12.5 萬人。 
分析師會參考該數據，推測美國政府的就業報告。美國 9 月就業報告定於週五公布。 
供應管理協會 (ISM) 公布 9 月非製造業指數上升至 59.8。預估為 55.5。 
分析師說，經濟數據強勁，且持續了很長時間。在反應颶風影響後，數據依舊強勁。預期聯準會 (Fed) 不僅將在 12 月升息，2018 年亦將進一步緊縮信用。 
週一與週二，主要指數亦均創新收盤高點，經濟數據強勁與稅改希望重燃，為利多。 
共和黨稅改行動，亦有助支撑股市。上週，共和黨推出稅改方案，將公司稅由 35% 降至 20%。 
但分析師並不確定共和黨的方案能否順利推動。這項計畫只是大綱，總統將之付諸國會，填補細節。

posts.title: Dirty Apron 學做菜
posts.text: My company subsidizes 80% of the $170 for mine. it was overall an excellent experience. (每人一日學費加幣$170，卡蜜爾的公司幫她付80%,眷屬小艾嘛，全額自付。學費不便宜喔，但經驗超值:-:-) We started at 11am and we cooked 3 dishes until 3 pm. We were served wine or beer as well. (教三道菜，時間自早上十一點到下午三點鐘。還有葡萄酒或啤酒配餐。Dessert是師傅做的) There were about 10-14 students there. It was very yummy! Yes,we will make you dinner when you come! We have the recipes! (真好呷！阿爹阿母返加時，孩子們要煮給父母吃。)

thread.title_full: Services Division, Corporate Services and Real Estate, Office Manager, Associate, Taipei

posts.title: Services Division, Corporate Services and Real Estate, Office Manager, Associate, Taipei
posts.text:
YOUR IMPACT 

Are you passionate about office management and driving productivity to enable the firm’s flow of business? We are looking for a professional to join our regional division who wants to use their skills and capabilities to ensure the smooth business operations of the Taipei Office of Goldman Sachs. 

CSRE’s office manager is responsible for the cost-effective and timely provision of all corporate services activities to the office. This role is the client interface between the office staff and the CSRE functions. The manager will be responsible for providing oversight for all facilities management processes and ensure the efficient provision of business services, including reception, mail, production, travel, purchasing, information management and facilities. 

How You Will Fulfill Your Potential 

Working with counterparts in other regional offices you will be responsible for coordinating the appropriate service requirements that the Taipei office will require. Specifically you will be responsible for: 
Manage all internal client relationships, ensuring that clients requirements are appropriately met in accordance to the firm’s guidelines in a timely and complete manner; Providing on-site leadership and coordination of all CSRE functions including real estate, business services and financial and administrative support ; Leading, managing and developing local CSRE team and vendor team to ensure smooth business operations in partnership with regional functional managers:- Oversee hospitality services including receptionist management, pantry provision, conference room management, and supporting internal and external events; Oversee document management services including mail operation, record retention processes and production support; Oversee all facilities management services and contracts, including routine moves/construction projects, building operations, cleaning, security and elevators; Oversee all on-site and off-site conferencing requirements for internal and client activities; Ensure quality provision of travel and ground transportation services, including ticket issuance procedures, refunds and adherence to travel policy; Manage the appropriate approval of all office purchases, including office supplies, corporate stationery, business machines (copiers, fax) and promotional products; Manage local vendors’ relationships and maintain management oversight; Representing the division in negotiation with internal client and external vendor; Maintain oversight of any risk areas to escalate and resolve in conjunction with regional counterparts; Provide regular postings to management on relevant operational updates

thread.title_full: Multi-Asset Investments - Intern (TAIWAN, 6 months)

posts.title: Multi-Asset Investments - Intern (TAIWAN, 6 months)
posts.text:
Multi-Asset Investments - Intern (TAIWAN, 6 months) 

Role Summary 
The role will be part of the Multi-Asset Investments function. The selected candidate will support the analytics and investment responsibility within the team. 
Key Responsibilities 
Supports and improves the research & trading effort by assisting in the portfolio oversight effort and by improving the availability, and visibility of data and analysis, thereby improving investment decisions, investment policy decisions and investment compliance. 
Assist the investment manager in streamlining the investment workflow. 
Helps the team to improve new methods of gathering, analysing, presenting and reporting investment performance, performance attribution, portfolio management processes, portfolio analytics, trading analytics. 
Maintains a superior level of accuracy and quality control at all times. 
Assists with the creation, processes and distribution of reports, presentations, charts, graphs and data extracts. 
Verifies the accuracy of data in various monthly and quarterly reports produced by the team. 
Responds to specific requests for investment and portfolio-related data. 
Assist with building and maintenance of quantitative research database.

thread.title: LINE貼圖半價 但熊大為此事道歉
thread.title_full: LINE貼圖半價 但熊大為此事道歉

posts.title: LINE貼圖半價 但熊大為此事道歉
posts.text: Ｌu's & H.H先生即日起至10/23貼圖半價，但在LINE貼圖最前線公告圖案卻無法連入半價貼圖，因此下方出現連結網址。手機截圖 LINE貼圖最前線今天公布，即日起至10/23限時4天，Ｌu's & H.H先生聯手出擊，共計有7款指定貼圖半價，只要50代幣即台幣30元。但刊出後不少人發現連結有問題，紛紛留言無法連結，後來LINE又貼出下載的連結網址，但原來的公告仍無法連結，且點入後會出現熊大道歉的畫面。若想下載Ｌu's & H.H先生7款指定貼圖半價，除可在LINE貼圖最前線提供第連結網址外，在貼圖小舖上也有活動頁可直接點入，目前半價貼圖最熱門的是H.H先生全螢幕貼圖─美美的少女日常，在官方貼圖排行第三，其次是H.H先生甜猩女神陪伴篇，排名第六。(王雪玲／綜合報導)

thread.title: Sea集團前往拜會何美玥國策顧問 鼓勵有助臺灣發展的投資案
thread.title_full: Sea集團前往拜會何美玥國策顧問 鼓勵有助臺灣發展的投資案

posts.title: Sea集團前往拜會何美玥國策顧問 鼓勵有助臺灣發展的投資案
posts.text:
Sea集團總裁Nick Nash昨(23)日下午拜訪總統府國策顧問何美玥與經濟部次長龔明鑫，雙方就台灣網路產業的未來發展進行意見交流。Sea集團旗下包含遊戲、電子商務與電子支付等業務，旗下Garena在東南亞及台灣營運英雄聯盟、傳說對決等多款知名遊戲，而蝦皮購物則為東南亞目前最大電商平台。 
會後何顧問表示，電子商務等相關領域都是新興產業，也是政府鼓勵的方向，對於有助於台灣整體發展的投資案，只要符合政策及相關法律規章，政府都予以正面看待。 

Nick總裁表示，台灣的網路產業發展蓬勃，是一個非常值得長期投資的市場。台灣有熱情且具創業精神的中小企業主，為我們的電商事業提供的良好的發展契機；另外我們有很多才華洋溢的電競選手，整體的人才更是非常優秀且具競爭力，我們非常期待並樂於長期耕耘台灣市場。 

Sea集團市場涵蓋東南亞及台灣七國，為該區域最大的網路科技公司，上周甫在美國紐約股市上市，是東南亞第一個在美股上市的網路公司。 Sea集團成立於2009年，經營三大業界領先的平台，包括數位遊戲、電子商務與數位金融服務。圖／Sea集團提供 
This afternoon (Oct. 23rd), Nick Nash, the President of Sea Group, met with Mei-Yuei Ho, Senior Advisor of President Tsai’s office, and Ming-Hsin Kung, Deputy Minister of Economic Affairs. The two parties had in-depth discussions on plans to further the Internet industry in Taiwan. Sea is the largest Internet company in Greater Southeast Asia with leadership presence in gaming, e-commerce and online payment. Their best-known games includes League of Legends (LoL) and Arena of Valor (AoV). Moreover, their e-commerce business, Shopee, has risen to the top platforms in Southeast Asia. 

Ho stated that Taiwanese government recognizes gaming and e-commerce are both booming in Taiwan and will continue to support the development in these industries. Taiwan welcomes any types of foreign investments as long as they stay within the courses of regulations and related laws. 

President Nick Nash also confirms long-term investment in Taiwan due to its thriving Internet industry. “The SMEs in Taiwan have proven track records in entrepreneurship. We also have many outstanding young e-sports players, not to mention the abundance of seasoned talents. We hired more than 500 talents in Taiwan. We are excited about committing ourselves in the market for the long run.” 

Sea’s operation covers seven countries in Southeast Asia and Taiwan and is currently the largest Internet technology company in the region. Last Friday, Sea announced its initial public offering in the New York Stock Exchange (NYSE), which made them the very first Internet company from Southeast Asia to be listed in the NYSE. 
(中時電子報)
